_source.body: Quotes, “Being able to break security doesn’t make you a hacker any more than being able to hotwire cars makes you an automotive engineer.” - Eric Raymond

_source.body:
THAT IS WHAT
HAPPENS WHEN A POLITICAN PLAYS GENERAL WITH CONTEMPT FOR AMERICANS SAFETY.

 Joe Biden and his administration seemed to refuse
and not accept the information from the professionals who predicted and
informed them about the imminent collapse of the Afghanistan government and
their security forces.

It seems that
the disastrous early pullout of the military and the abandonment of Bagram
Airfield has jeopardized Americans and the Afghans who supported the US. 

The lack of
foresight of the Biden administration to realize that the 5000 ISIS Al-QAEDA
terrorists and prisoners would be released from prison. Did they murder our
soldiers??

THE BUCK DOES
STOPS HERE WITH JOE BIDEN AND THE BIDEN ADMINISTRATION WHO DECISIONS NOW SEEM TO
BE DIRECTLY RESPONSIBLE FOR AMERICAN MILITARY DEATHS AND HUNDREDS OF OTHERS.

Bagram
Airfield it seems was much more defensible than Kabul Airport is and now the
unnecessary deaths of 13 American soldiers have paid the price for someone who
believes he is the savior of America.

THE BIDEN
ADMINISTRATION ALREADY REFERRED THIS AIRLIFT TO THE HISTIORAL BERLIN AIRLIFT
SHOWS THE COMPTEMT THEY SHOW FOR AMERICAN INTELLGENCE AS EVERYONE WITH COMMON
SENSE KNOWS THE ONLY REASON IS THE LACK OF COMPETENCY WITHIN THE BIDEN
ADMINISTRATION CAUSED A NEED FOR THE FRANTIC SCENES SEEN DAILY AT THE AIRPORT.
THE MILITARY IS ON THE FRONT LINES IN KABUL, NOT ANY POLITICANS.

The higher
brass of the military will forever be considered cowards if they do not publicly
stand up to Job Biden even if they have to resign immediately after doing so. IF
SOMEONE IN THE MILITARY FALLS ASLEEP IN TIME OF WAR, WHICH WE HAVE BEEN FOR 20
YEARS THE PENTALY IS DEATH OR A COURT MARTIAL.

Bagram
Airfield was abandoned without any of the following military brass publicly
objecting to what was most likely known by them that you never leave Americans
or our allies behind by capitulating to the enemy giving them the upper hand. One
of the biggest military blunders in the history of the US

Llyod Austin is the Secretary of Defense 41
years

General Charles Brown is the Chief of Staff of
the Air Force 36 years

General James McConville is the Chief of Staff
of the Army 30 years

Admiral Michael Gilday is the Chief of Naval
Operations 36 years

General John Raymond is the Chief of Space
Operations 37 years

General Daniel Hokanson is the Chief of the
National Guard Bureau 34 years

 

It does not take a military genius to know that
Bagram Airfield never should never been abandoned until all Americans and their
allies were safely evacuated

 

Joe Biden
nor his administration are not military geniuses. Everybody can see with

their own eyes they are amateurs, inept and incompetent especially,
after losing American military lives along with hundreds of others 

 

Trumps tweets
sometime were offensive, vulgar at times, but he would never leave Americans at
the mercy of the enemy which seems will happen on August 31st by the
Biden Administration

It seems that
thousands of Americans and our allies will be stranded by Joe Biden leaving most
at the mercy of the US enemies 

THAT IS WHAT
HAPPENS WHEN A POLITICAN PLAY GENERAL WITH CONTEMPT FOR AMERICANS SAFETY.

LET NANCY
PELOSI AND CHUCK SCHUMER NOW DO WHAT THEY HAVE BEEN TRYING FOR SEVERAL YEARS TO
TRUMP INVESTIGATE AND CONVICT AS THE PROOF IS RIGHT IN FRONT OF YOU AS EVERYONE
ALREADY SEES THE PROOF IS THERE

There is no
unidentified whistle blower or manufactured evidence by Adam Schiff or Eric
Swalwell who said he has ample evidence but never found or showed it.
